0g073a56305174": ["|Sure! Show me around|", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders_Wildshape.html", "70d846c0-cc10-42d6-9814-34d6318eaeff"], "h384f98a5g8fc0g4273gbaafg9dd0281d4aba": ["|*House tour follows*|", "c3184d85-1e3f-4e64-85bd-5841fef2e27a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders_Wildshape.html", "600a43c4-5f9c-4a48-a2dd-e77d091772b4"], "hc2e46327ge1a8g461dg88b8g84690207c970": ["|*Take your leave*|", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders_Wildshape.html", "f605903c-2e53-470c-b506-da045e0447f1"], "hb99134bcgf9d6g4f80gb47cg4756c7911f29": ["|Greetings unknown animal|", "c3184d85-1e3f-4e64-85bd-5841fef2e27a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders_Wildshape.html", "3e72cd7e-a141-487d-8755-43ae2fcd1edc"], "h9abba57egb4e7g40e8g8c5dg88db6117450d": ["|We generally eat people and other animals that end up here|", "c3184d85-1e3f-4e64-85bd-5841fef2e27a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders_Wildshape.html", "219d3259-c49a-48bd-95d3-90e415568b3b"], "h0f8d3041g6f06g43eega8cfg3595ebf00c4b": ["|So... prepare to get eated!|", "c3184d85-1e3f-4e64-85bd-5841fef2e27a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders_Wildshape.html", "27c1ba4f-456d-4306-bdec-77ee95b315e4"], "h5d738e3dg26c5g474bg8e10ge367c0066a45": ["|Eated! Eated! Is it eated or eaten, sis?|", "03d2278d-f1fa-41ff-bdbe-03045725d990", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders_Wildshape.html", "149fe75e-6f94-45b0-8f57-f419ac5c354e"], "h403c992ag8c87g4396g828dg2b2ff6c0ece0": ["|But wait! Goblins are so much tastier and with our animal forces combined, we can get a feast unlike anything you had!|", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders_Wildshape.html", "50901685-d5fb-4d81-8608-4e26ccd933f5"], "h275be863g0f86g4e5ag9c2bg5eea6072ab7d": ["|At least you recognize us as animals. Refreshing!|", "c3184d85-1e3f-4e64-85bd-5841fef2e2